    },
    {
      "text": "Every shipment tendered to a Carrier by BacklotCars will be subject to the terms of the BacklotCars Broker-Carrier Agreement;",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 3.79,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 1880,
      "char_end": 2005
    },
    {
      "text": "BacklotCars' Terms and Conditions, to the extent applicable which are posted online at (www.backlotcars.com); and applicable",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.15,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2006,
      "char_end": 2130
    },
    {
      "text": "law.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.52,
        "width": 0.3,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2131,
      "char_end": 2135
    },
    {
      "text": "In the event of a conflict between the terms and provisions of the BacklotCars Broker-Carrier Agreement and the BacklotCars'",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.88,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2136,
      "char_end": 2260
    },
    {
      "text": "Terms and Conditions, the terms and provisions of the Agreement shall control.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.25,
        "width": 6.2,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2261,
      "char_end": 2339
    },
    {
      "text": "Documentation and General Procedures:",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.62,
        "width": 3.0,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2340,
      "char_end": 2377
    },
    {
      "text": "1. Carrier should contact customers at least two (2) hours prior to pick up or delivery of a vehicle to schedule a convenient time",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.98,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2378,
      "char_end": 2508
    },
    {
      "text": "during normal business hours for access. Failure to schedule an appointment may result in a missed or delayed pick up or",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.35,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2509,
      "char_end": 2629
    },
    {
      "text": "delivery. BacklotCars will not incur any dry run fees as a result of Carrier's failure to schedule an appointment.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.71,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2630,
      "char_end": 2744
    },
    {
      "text": "2. In the event that Carrier is unable to perform the requested Services, Carrier shall notify BacklotCars within one (1) day after",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 7.08,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2745,
      "char_end": 2876
    },
    {
      "text": "Carrier determines it is unable to perform the requested Services.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 7.44,
        "width": 5.3,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2877,
      "char_end": 2943
    },
    {
      "text": "3. Carrier shall not disclose or discuss the terms of the BacklotCars Broker-Carrier Agreement including the rates or the",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 7.81,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 2944,
      "char_end": 3065
    },
    {
      "text": "valuation of the Services with customers or other third parties.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 8.17,
        "width": 5.1,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3066,
      "char_end": 3130
    },
    {
      "text": "4. Carrier will be responsible for loading and unloading all shipments. Carrier must utilize appropriate equipment, including a",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 8.54,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3131,
      "char_end": 3258
    },
    {
      "text": "winch for inoperable vehicles, when loading and unloading vehicles.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 8.9,
        "width": 5.4,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3259,
      "char_end": 3326
    },
    {
      "text": "5. Carrier must verify that the vehicle identification number (VIN) on the BacklotCars dispatch paperwork matches the VIN on",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 9.27,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3327,
      "char_end": 3451
    },
    {
      "text": "the vehicle. Any discrepancies must be reported to BacklotCars prior to pick up.",
      "page_number": 2,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 9.63,
        "width": 6.4,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3452,
      "char_end": 3532
    },
    {
      "text": "6. Carrier shall not, under any circumstances aside from loading and unloading, drive any vehicle consigned to them unless",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 0.5,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3534,
      "char_end": 3656
    },
    {
      "text": "given specific approval from BacklotCars. Driving vehicles without authorization will result in non-payment of carriage as well as",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 0.9,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3657,
      "char_end": 3787
    },
    {
      "text": "any additional BacklotCars Customer imposed penalties (including, but not limited to, additional mileage charges).",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 1.3,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3788,
      "char_end": 3902
    },
    {
      "text": "7. Carrier shall provide evidence of pickup in the form designated by BacklotCars indicating the quantity of vehicles picked up,",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 1.7,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 3903,
      "char_end": 4031
    },
    {
      "text": "a description of each vehicle including its condition, odometer reading, BacklotCars Order ID, VIN(s), and the legible name and",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 2.1,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4032,
      "char_end": 4159
    },
    {
      "text": "signature of a representative of the pickup location.",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 2.5,
        "width": 4.2,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4160,
      "char_end": 4213
    },
    {
      "text": "8. Carrier will deliver all vehicles to the appropriate destination as listed on the pickup notice. Carrier shall be liable for any",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 2.9,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4214,
      "char_end": 4345
    },
    {
      "text": "damages resulting from delivery at an alternative destination.",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 3.3,
        "width": 5.0,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4346,
      "char_end": 4408
    },
    {
      "text": "9. Carrier shall provide to BacklotCars, within twenty-four (24) hours of delivery, an invoice and detailed condition report",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 3.7,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4409,
      "char_end": 4533
    },
    {
      "text": "containing the quantity of vehicles delivered, a description of each vehicle and its condition, VIN(s), and acknowledgement of",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.1,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4534,
      "char_end": 4660
    },
    {
      "text": "delivery by the recipient of the shipment, including the recipient's legible name and signature.",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.5,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4661,
      "char_end": 4757
    },
    {
      "text": "10. BacklotCars pays Carrier, via ACH, all complete and undisputed amounts set forth in each Carrier invoice in full within thirty",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 4.9,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4758,
      "char_end": 4888
    },
    {
      "text": "(30) days from the date of BacklotCars' receipt of the invoice.",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.3,
        "width": 5.0,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4889,
      "char_end": 4952
    },
    {
      "text": "Powered by Super Dispatch",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 5.7,
        "width": 2.0,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4953,
      "char_end": 4978
    },
    {
      "text": "This agreement is made by and between a \"Carrier\" and a \"Broker / Shipper\". Super Dispatch",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.1,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 4979,
      "char_end": 5069
    },
    {
      "text": "Inc. and its affiliates are not party to this agreement. Super Dispatch Inc. and affiliates",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.5,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 5070,
      "char_end": 5161
    },
    {
      "text": "have no obligation under this agreement and expressly disclaim any and all liability and",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 6.9,
        "width": 6.5,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 5162,
      "char_end": 5250
    },
    {
      "text": "warranties arising out of, or in connection with this agreement.",
      "page_number": 3,
      "bounding_box": {
        "x": 1.0,
        "y": 7.3,
        "width": 5.1,
        "height": 0.25
      },
      "char_start": 5251,
      "char_end": 5315
    }
  ]
}
